38:58.003 --> 38:59.635
- It's pink.

38:59.671 --> 39:02.505
The same colour we've been
seeing coming out of mexico.

39:02.640 --> 39:05.908
- Take it. Get it tested to see
if it's the same stuff.

39:06.978 --> 39:09.245
- Um, have you heard
who adam gentle is?

39:10.449 --> 39:13.249
An accountant. Real nerd.
Lives on derwyn drive.

39:13.285 --> 39:16.386
- No. Is that
who marc's been calling?

39:17.789 --> 39:20.723
- Yeah, but I still can't find
out what the connection is.

39:20.726 --> 39:23.593
Accountants, bikers,
3d guns, mexico.

39:23.595 --> 39:26.328
I have no clue what is going on.

39:26.365 --> 39:28.097
- Want to walk it through
together?

39:29.401 --> 39:30.800
(sighing)

39:30.869 --> 39:33.602
Ah, yes. Nah, it's cool.
Let's leave it.

39:33.638 --> 39:36.005
- Yeah. Yeah.

39:37.209 --> 39:39.809
- At least I took care
of those hiccups.

39:39.811 --> 39:42.077
Oh.
(laughing)

39:45.117 --> 39:47.516
- Uh, hey.
Do you still eat pizza?

39:48.653 --> 39:50.353
Or are you one of those
gluten-free nerds now?

39:50.488 --> 39:52.689
- Oh, hell, no.
(car horn honking)

39:52.824 --> 39:55.692
- I mean, I figure we could
go to guarducci's on 3rd,

39:55.827 --> 39:57.226
Talk it out.

39:58.696 --> 40:00.262
- After you.

40:04.903 --> 40:08.037
- So, okay, this is what
I figured out so far.

40:08.106 --> 40:11.307
It's three main gangs
that are in this.

40:11.376 --> 40:12.975
We've got sons of jupiter...

40:33.264 --> 40:36.131
- Did you... Get what you needed
outta that phone, or...?

40:38.370 --> 40:42.405
I'm sorry... It's pretty good
we got it back, though. Right?

40:43.775 --> 40:45.875
It's, like, better than some
random criminal having it--

40:45.944 --> 40:47.409
- You know what would've
been better?

40:47.446 --> 40:49.145
Not having had it stolen
in the first place,

40:49.214 --> 40:50.846
As retribution
for you dealing drugs.

40:50.882 --> 40:52.248
That, elliot,

40:52.250 --> 40:53.750
That would've been better.

40:55.821 --> 40:59.588
- I'm sorry.
I'm... I'm really sorry.

41:02.227 --> 41:04.394
Can I make you dinner
or something? Or...

41:04.396 --> 41:05.528
Like, run you a bath?

41:05.664 --> 41:08.298
(sam chuckling)
- uh, you could...

41:08.433 --> 41:09.965
Stop dealing drugs.

41:10.001 --> 41:12.368
Get a job. Go to university.

41:12.370 --> 41:14.036
There's really so much
that you could do. Not...

41:14.072 --> 41:16.439
Not really for me,
but for you, elliot.

41:16.508 --> 41:18.641
(soft piano music)

41:35.861 --> 41:40.597
♪ rain pouring down
my head pounds from the sound ♪

41:40.599 --> 41:44.534
♪ I'm stuck to the bed
with brain zaps... ♪

41:44.536 --> 41:46.702
- You look like an idiot
when you smoke.

41:47.939 --> 41:51.073
- Doesn't everyone?
♪ I'm trying hard to change ♪

41:51.109 --> 41:53.476
♪ I wish I knew why ♪

41:53.611 --> 41:56.546
♪ I always stay the same ♪

41:58.016 --> 42:03.419
♪ this is not who I want... ♪

42:03.488 --> 42:05.821
♪ to be... ♪
- elliot tell you what happened?

42:05.857 --> 42:08.524
- Yeah, he did. He did.

42:11.229 --> 42:13.696
- How do I teach him
about consequences...

42:15.767 --> 42:17.500
...When they never
seem to find him?

42:19.537 --> 42:22.505
- Maybe he never had
a mother who...

42:22.574 --> 42:24.640
Let him land on his ass.

42:30.682 --> 42:32.748
- You got it all figured out,
huh?

42:33.585 --> 42:35.851
- Don't be stupid, samantha.

42:36.988 --> 42:39.154
Nobody has it all figured out.

42:44.796 --> 42:46.262
(judy sighing)

42:48.466 --> 42:49.999
Got another one of those?

43:01.079 --> 43:02.478
Light?

43:04.282 --> 43:05.882
(soft music continues)

43:14.893 --> 43:17.426
Subtitling: Difuze
